				<div class="post-heading">
					<h1>No Furby App for Kindle Fire (Updated)</h1>
					<span class="heading-author">Eric</span> 
					<span class="heading-date">April 7, 2013</span>
					<span class="heading-comments"><a href="http://www.furbymanual.com/no-furby-app-for-kindle-fire/#comments" title="Comment on No Furby App for Kindle Fire (Updated)">96</a></span>
				</div>
				
								
								
												
				<div class="post-entry">
										
					<p><!-- AdSense Now! V4.33 --><br />
<!-- Post[leadin] --></p>
<div class="adsense adsense-leadin" style="text-align:center;margin: 12px;"><script type="text/javascript"><!--
google_ad_client = "ca-pub-1470353520081367";
/* FurbyManualMain */
google_ad_slot = "5106505393";
google_ad_width = 468;
google_ad_height = 15;
//-->
</script><br />
<script type="text/javascript"
src="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js">
</script></div>
<p><!-- AdSense Now! V4.33 --><br />
&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"> See also: </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5em;"><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.furbymanual.com/?p=876">Kindle Fire &amp; the Furby App</a> </strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em;">Bad news for Kindle Fire owners.  After emailing Hasbro directly to inquire when the Furby app may become available, I received my answer </span><em style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em;"><strong>&#8221; There are no current plans to add the Furby App to the Kindle Fire&#8221;.</strong>  </em><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em;"> Does that mean there will never be a Kindle Fire app? Not necessarily.  If enough Kindle users show interest, anything is possible.  But at the moment however, its a no go.  Its not a total loss though,  Furbies work fine without an app or connected device, the app just adds a few extra &#8216;bells and whistles&#8217; such as feeding graphic images of food to Furby, and a Furbish to English translator.  </span></h1>
<p>You want the Furby App for Kindle Fire?  Let Hasbro know and post your comments below!<!-- AdSense Now! V4.33 --><br />
<!-- Post[leadout] --></p>
<div class="adsense adsense-leadout" style="text-align:center;margin: 12px;"><script type="text/javascript"><!--
